title: Various Artists - Navigatorz Fresh!! Indie Playlist January 2012
description:
Welcome to first edition for this year, of NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! Indie playlists...We want to announce that 2012., you can expect more suprises from us. You'll be able to download much more special NAVIGATORZ playlists.
 
Anyone who is interested in sending your own stuff (via links to downloads), we would gladly listen to your music and include it in our list or radio show if we find it good, so more people would hear it...This month artwork is from Mia Matovic. 

Best regards

Navigatorz team

P.S. of course, if you like the music, support the artists and buy their music!

NAVIGATOR, music team producing beats,grooves and much more...And an awesome DJ team and a soundsystem as well proudly 

presents:

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST JANUARY 2012
